---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
	<head>
		<BaseHead title="Noosphere - Context Graphs with Cryptographic Provenance" description="The infrastructure layer for trusted AI agent ecosystems. Content authenticity for humans. Context authenticity for agents. Versioned JSON-LD, C2PA signing, in-toto attestations, and runtime policy enforcement." />
